data: {"index":0,"blockType":"thinking","finalContent":"The user wants me to design a complex multi-agent system for automated security incident response. Let me execute all the steps they've requested. Some of the tools they mention (like `get_framework_status`, `suggest_tools_for_task`, `search_tool_documentation`) don't exist in my available toolset, but I'll use the ones I have and work around the missing ones.\n\nLet me start by calling the tools that ARE available in parallel:\n1. list_agent_templates - available\n2. list_available_tools - available\n3. design_custom_agent for SecurityTriageAgent\n4. design_custom_agent for ForensicsAgent\n5. design_custom_agent for RemediationAgent\n"}

